<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.3.4">
<l>pīḷai cōrak kaṇṇi ṭuṅkippit teḻa mūttirumi</l>
<l>tāḷkaḷ nōvat tammil muṭṭit taḷḷi naṭavāmuṉ</l>
<l>kāḷai yākik kaṉṟu mēyttuk kuṉṟeṭut taṉṟuniṉṟāṉ</l>
<l>vāḷai pāyun taṇṭa ṭañcūḻ vatari vaṇaṅkutumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Before I walk shuffling, knocking [my] knees together so they ache,</l>
<l>Squinting [my] eyes as rheum oozes, coughing [from] age so that phlegm rises,</l>
<l>We will worship at Badarī, encircled by cool ponds where vāḷai [fish] leap,</l>
<l>Of him who, having grazed the calves as a youth,</l>
<l rend="indent">then stood lifting a mountain.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
